debug_steps.name: Understand the System
debug_steps.llm_analysis: The test is failing because of an AttributeError: __name__. This happens when trying to access the __name__ attribute on a mock function. In the with_retry decorator, it's trying to use func.__name__ but since the function is a MagicMock object, it doesn't have this attribute by default. The solution would be to ensure the mock has a __name__ attribute or modify the decorator to handle this case.
